        Building Management Statements in Queensland: What Sellers of Mixed-Use Properties Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A building management statement is a registered document that applies to mixed-use buildings. Here is what sellers in these developments need to understand before going to market.
      </p>
    </div>
